ALTHOUGH I HAD COPIES, THEY WERE RESISTANT TO ACCEPT THEM, ESPECIALLY SINCE THEY HAD ALREADY PAID OUT THE ANNUITY. I FELT I MADE THE NECESSARY EFFORTS TO EXECUTE THIS CLIENT'S REQUEST.
